data.description: The possibilities are endless if you look at the big picture! Stop by and take a glance at this home in the Callalen School District. This 3 bedroom,  1 bath home is just over 1200 sqft. with a 2 car attached garage.   The oversized backyard is great for entertaining and fun activities for everyone. Don't miss out on your opportunity to make this home yours.
